I haven't really noticed anyone preaching anything, in a way I started the thread to possibly give a nudge in the right direction to some who look at EQ as their life and are allowing it to control them, and when it's gone they realize they have nothing left.  Don't be caught in that situation, I wouldn't wish that on my worst enemy.<br>
