<br>
It seems to me that a lot of people are in denial about EQ or computer addiction too. I understand there are people with physical disabilities that find refuge in EQ because they feel more comfortable in it than living a more active life style, and I think maybe thats the best option for them. <br>
<br>
Don't get me wrong, EQ is definitely good in reasonable amounts. It's good for the mind. I find my imagination wanders a lot into very interesting thoughts while I play.<br>
